fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(
  AND(
    MONTH( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ) = 2,
    DAY( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ) = 29,
    NOT( 
      OR( 
        MOD( YEAR( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ), 400 ) = 0, 
        AND( 
          MOD( YEAR( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ), 4 ) = 0,
          MOD( YEAR( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ), 100 ) != 0
        )
      )
    ) 
  ),
  DATE( YEAR( mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ) + 2, 3, 1),
  DATE( YEAR(  mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ) + 2, MONTH(  mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ), DAY(  mvp_Last_Tax_Review_Date__c ) )
)
